    <title>Data Visualization 2</title>
    <link href="/2023/08/01/dv2/"/>
    <url>/2023/08/01/dv2/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="Data-Visualization-2"><a href="#Data-Visualization-2" class="headerlink" title="Data Visualization 2"></a>Data Visualization 2</h1><p><strong>Fact</strong> : To see an object change, it’s necessary to attend to it. </p><h2 id="Workflow"><a href="#Workflow" class="headerlink" title="Workflow"></a>Workflow</h2><ul><li>数据平台</li><li>数据储存</li><li>数据获取</li><li>数据分析和处理</li><li>数据可视化</li></ul><h2 id="Data-Profiling"><a href="#Data-Profiling" class="headerlink" title="Data Profiling"></a>Data Profiling</h2><h4 id="Data-Overview"><a href="#Data-Overview" class="headerlink" title="Data Overview"></a>Data Overview</h4><ul><li>Data Domain</li><li>Data Description</li><li>Data Schema</li><li>Data Type</li><li>Data Range</li><li>Data Distribution</li><li>Data Quality<ul><li>Missing</li><li>Abnormal</li><li>Over-bounding</li><li>Redundant</li><li>Inconsistent</li></ul></li></ul><h4 id="Data-Wrangling"><a href="#Data-Wrangling" class="headerlink" title="Data Wrangling"></a>Data Wrangling</h4><p>The process of cleaning and transforming messy and complex data into a desired format to make it easier.</p><ul><li>Data Transformations<ul><li>Sorting 排序</li><li>Filtering 筛选</li><li>Distinct 去重</li><li>Slicing 分割</li><li>Extracting 提取</li><li>Mutating 转化</li><li>Replacing 替换</li><li>Spliting 分割</li><li>Merging 合并</li><li>Aggregating</li><li>Reshaping</li><li>Join 表链接</li></ul></li><li>Data Modeling<ul><li>Data Operators<ul><li>ETL</li><li>Feature Engineering</li><li>Machine Learning</li></ul></li></ul></li></ul><h2 id="Tableau-入门"><a href="#Tableau-入门" class="headerlink" title="Tableau 入门"></a>Tableau 入门</h2><p>Tableau is a business intellingence tool for visually analyzing the data</p><h4 id="Features"><a href="#Features" class="headerlink" title="Features"></a>Features</h4><ul><li>Support powerful data discovery and exploration</li><li>Easy to use</li></ul>]]></content>
    
    
